{"tid":2188624,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台助流亡港人預算增七倍","createTime":"2020-09-04T10:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T10:57:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd08c8c83c15194a9b4a01d67b11bba1eec01719","tid":2188624,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/E4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FE4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cfYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=33c34256\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FE4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA%2F&h=82acaf34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/E4F6BR5MNRC6NNHAMWMV5ETFJA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n台助流亡港人預算增七倍<br />\n<br />\n因應中央在香港實施港版國安法，台灣陸委會今年7月設立台港服務交流辦公室，執掌該辦公室的台港策進會今年度的預算大幅增加，比往年大增七倍至4,100萬元新台幣（約1,080萬港元）。陸委會指出，增加的預算將用於港人在台就學就業的生活照顧及輔導。<br />\n<br />\n台港服務交流辦公室今年7月1日開始營運，台港經濟文化合作策進會負責。陸。。。<br />\n<br />\n據台港策進會公佈的年度預算書，明年度預算將提升至4,108萬餘元，比今年度。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v9ccG5KzI3ioHQQUzjhzfdyt1jw=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A5WCW3566BG7DHEEPEFC6MHDDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv9ccG5KzI3ioHQQUzjhzfdyt1jw%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA5WCW3566BG7DHEEPEFC6MHDDE.jpg&h=8cdd4d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■抗爭食堂「保護傘」半年前在台灣開業，為流亡港人提供工作機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陸委會拒評偷渡個案<br />\n<br />\n邱垂正也指出，辦公室今年度的支出被計入陸委會預算，明年度則會特別編列相關預算，讓辦公室能正常運作。他提到，相關預算由政府委託策進會，再由策進會交由辦公室使用。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒問及香港年輕人偷渡赴台時，邱則指出，政府對港人已設立人道援助機制，。。。<br />\n<br />\n邱垂正又希望外界勿作不必要揣測，並重申陸委會不鼓勵非法來台。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"}]}